data.title: What are some songs by cascada?
data.meta_description: Answers is the place to go to get the answers you need and to ask the questions you want
data.text:
What are Cascada's top songs?

She has a lot of songs, but some of her more populer ones are everytime we toutch, miracle,bad boy,ready or not, and most popular, evacuate the dance floor.

Does cascada write her own songs?

Cascada isn't a her, it's the whole band. There's like 4 of them in the band. The girl's name is Nathalie. No they don't, they just cover older songs from artist. "Just Like A Pill" was originally by P!nk and "Everytime We Touch" is originally by Maggie Reilly.

Who is Cascada?

Cascada is a German group. there are 3 people in this group and their names are Yanou and DJ Manian. One of her most famous songs is : " Every Time We Touch " and also "evacuate the dance floor" that came out this past year. To listen to it, go on YouTube, and type it on the search bar. please!!! they are very good songs thx u and thx u 4 using ask.com!!!!!!! ^^
